       New Construction and Additions
   title bar
     * New construction is generally assessable and may increase the
   taxable value of your property.
       Examples include:
   worker
       New room additions,
       pools, spas and patio covers

                                                               Next Button

     * Normal maintenance and repairs will not increase your taxable
   value.

   Examples include:

   A new roof or garage door.
